            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~djh101010" class="author" title="author name and user ID">djh101010 (656795) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3655223&cid=43468809">(#43468809)</a></h4>
